| POST 📤 | `/api/v1/auth/login`              | Login with credentials 🔑 | Public 🌍      |
| POST 📤 | `/api/v1/auth/logout`             | Logout (clears cookies) 🚪 | Authenticated 🔐 |
| POST 📤 | `/api/v1/auth/magic-link/send`    | Send magic link 🪄         | Public 🌍      |
| POST 📤 | `/api/v1/auth/google-login`       | Login with Google/Firebase 🔥 | Public 🌍   |

### 👩‍🎓📚 Student Management
| Method ⚡ | Endpoint 🔗                               | Description 📋                    | Access 🛡️      |
