| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/{id}`               | Fetch student by ID 🆔             | ADMIN 👑, TEACHER 👩‍🏫 |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/number/{number}`    | Fetch by student number 🔢         | ADMIN 👑, TEACHER 👩‍🏫 |
| PUT 🔄  | `/api/v1/students/{id}`               | Update student profile ✏️          | ADMIN 👑        |
| DELETE 🗑️ | `/api/v1/students/{id}`            | Soft delete student 🚫             | ADMIN 👑        |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/count`              | Count active students 🔢           | ADMIN 👑        |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/search`             | Search & filter (all properties) 🔍 | ADMIN 👑, TEACHER 👩‍🏫 |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/fee-defaulters`     | List fee defaulters ⚠️             | ADMIN 👑, ACCOUNTANT 💼 |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/boarders`           | List boarders by hostel 🏠          | ADMIN 👑        |
| GET 📥  | `/api/v1/students/scholarships`       | List scholarship students 🎓       | ADMIN 👑, ACCOUNTANT 💼 |

