## 🔐🛡️ Security & Authentication

This API implements a **multi-layer authentication strategy** 🧱🔒:

### 🔑🪙 JWT Authentication
- 🟢 Access token: **1 hour** expiry stored in `HttpOnly` cookie 🍪
- 🔵 Refresh token: **7 days** expiry stored in `HttpOnly` cookie 🍪
- 🔴 Tokens are **blacklisted in Redis** on logout 🚫

### 🔥☁️ Firebase Google Authentication
- 🌐 Supports Google Sign-In via Firebase
- ✅ Firebase token verified server-side 🖥️
- 👤 User auto-created if first login 🆕

### 📧🪄 OTP & Magic Link
- 🔒 OTP hashed with **BCrypt** and stored in DB with expiry ⏳
- 📬 Magic link sent via **Mailtrap** with HTML email templates 🎨

### 👥🎭 Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
- 🏷️ 27 roles supported: `ADMIN` 👑, `SUPER_ADMIN` 🌟, `PRINCIPAL` 🎓, `ACCOUNTANT` 💼, `CASHIER` 💰, `STUDENT` 🎒, `TEACHER` 👩‍🏫, and more
- 🔒 Each endpoint is protected by specific role combinations 🛡️

---

## 🗄️📊 Database Schema

### 🚀📋 Flyway Migrations (in order)
| Version 🔢 | File 📄                                  | Description 📋                 |
|---------|----------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| V1 1️⃣    | `V1__create_users_table.sql`           | Users table + `user_role` enum 👤 |
| V2 2️⃣    | `V2__create_student_profiles_table.sql`| Student profiles + all enums 🎓  |
| V3 3️⃣    | `V3__create_payment_tables.sql`        | Student accounts + fee payments 💳|

### 💡💰 Money Handling
> ⚠️🔢 All monetary values use `NUMERIC(19, 2)` in PostgreSQL 🐘 and `BigDecimal` in Java ☕.
> 🚫 **Floating-point types (`double`, `float`) are never used for currency** to prevent precision errors 🎯.

---

## 💳⚡ Stripe Payment Integration

### 💰🔄 Payment Flow
```
🖥️ Frontend (Angular)
    │
    ├─ 1️⃣ Collect card details via Stripe.js Elements 💳
    ├─ 2️⃣ Create PaymentMethod → receive paymentMethodId 🔑
    └─ 3️⃣ POST /one-time-fee-payment { studentNumber, paymentAmount, paymentMethodId, currency } 📤
                │
                └─ 🖥️ Backend (Spring Boot)
                        ├─ 4️⃣ Validate student + account ✅
                        ├─ 5️⃣ Calculate incentive + new balance 🧮
                        ├─ 6️⃣ Calculate next due date 📅
                        ├─ 7️⃣ Create Stripe PaymentIntent 💳
                        ├─ 8️⃣ Confirm PaymentIntent with paymentMethodId 🔐
                        ├─ 9️⃣ On success → update balance + save FeePayment record ✅💰
                        └─ 🔟 Return full payment response 📤
```

### 🃏🧪 Stripe Test Cards
| Card Number 💳         | Scenario 🎭              |
|----------------------|-----------------------|
| `4242 4242 4242 4242` | ✅ Payment succeeds 🎉   |
| `4000 0000 0000 0002` | ❌ Payment declined 🚫   |
| `4000 0025 0000 3155` | 🔐 Requires 3D Secure 🛡️ |

