## 🚀🏁 Getting Started

### 📋✅ Prerequisites
- ☕ Java 21+
- 🐘 PostgreSQL 15+
- 🔴 Redis (via WSL on Windows or Docker 🐳)
- 🐳 Docker & Docker Compose (optional)
- 🔑 Stripe account (test mode) 💳
- ☁️ Cloudinary account 📸
- 🔥 Firebase project
- 📧 Mailtrap account 📬

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository 📦
```bash
git clone https://github.com/asohyannick/studentFeeOneTimePayment.git
cd studentFeeOneTimePayment
```

### 2️⃣ Configure Environment Variables ⚙️
Create a `.env` file in the project root (see [Environment Variables](#-environment-variables) section) 📄.

### 3️⃣ Start Redis (WSL) 🔴
```bash
# In WSL terminal 💻
sudo service redis-server start

# Verify Redis is running ✅
redis-cli -a yourpassword ping  # Should return PONG 🏓
```

### 4️⃣ Run the Application ▶️
```bash
# Build and run 🔨▶️
mvn clean install
mvn spring-boot:run

# Or with a specific profile 🎯
mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=dev
```

### 5️⃣ Access Swagger UI 📖
```
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html 🌐
```

