## ⚙️🔧 Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file or set these in `application-dev.yml` 📄:

```env
# ─── 🚀 Application ──────────────────────────────────────
APP_NAME=studentFeeOneTimePayment
SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=dev
PORT=8080
API_VERSION=v1

# ─── 🗄️ Database ─────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_PORT=5432
DATABASE_NAME=student_fee_db
DATABASE_USER=postgres
DATABASE_PASSWORD=yourpassword

# ─── 🔴 Redis ────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_HOST=127.0.0.1
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=yourredispassword
REDIS_TTL_MINUTES=30

# ─── 🔐 JWT ──────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET_KEY=your-256-bit-secret-key-here
JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRATION_MS=3600000
JWT_REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRATION_MS=604800000

# ─── 💳 Stripe ───────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_API_KEY=sk_test_your_stripe_secret_key

# ─── ☁️ Cloudinary ───────────────────────────────────────
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_api_key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_api_secret

# ─── 📧 Mailtrap ─────────────────────────────────────────
MAILTRAP_API_TOKEN=your_mailtrap_token
MAIL_FROM=noreply@leedtech.com
MAIL_FROM_NAME=LeedTech

# ─── 🔥 Firebase ─────────────────────────────────────────
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY_ID=your_key_id
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=your_service_account_email
FIREBASE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id

# ─── 🌐 CORS ─────────────────────────────────────────────
FRONTEND_DOMAINS=http://localhost:4200
ALLOWED_METHODS=GET,POST,PUT,DELETE,OPTIONS

# ─── 🌱 Seeder (one per role) ────────────────────────────
SEED_ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@leedtech.com
SEED_ADMIN_PASSWORD=Admin@123456
SEED_STUDENT_EMAIL=student@leedtech.com
SEED_STUDENT_PASSWORD=Student@123456
# ... (27 total, one per role) 🔢
```

